Layout Class	                   Purpose
BoxLayout	   ----------------   Arranges widgets in a vertical or horizontal box.
GridLayout   ----------------   rranges widgets in a grid of rows and columns.
StackLayout  ----------------	  Places widgets next to each other until no space is left, then wraps.
FloatLayout  ----------------   Places widgets at absolute positions using pos and size_hint.
AnchorLayout ---------------- 	Anchors widgets to top, bottom, center, etc.
RelativeLayout --------------   Positions widgets relative to their parent layout.
ScatterLayout	----------------  Used to rotate, scale, drag widgets — for gestures.
PageLayout  ------------------	For creating multi-page swipeable views.
ScrollView   -------------------	Enables scrolling — usually wraps another layout.
 
